    },
    "featureBullets": [
      "CUSHION FOUNDATION WITH NATURAL RADIANT FINISH & SKIN-LIKE TEXTURE: Created by renowned Korean makeup artist Jung Saem Mool, a pioneer in \u201cglass skin\u201d and natural complexion makeup, this cushion foundation delivers a dewy glow that mimics healthy, real skin. Known for decades of backstage experience, Jung\u2019s artistry ensures flawless results for daily foundation routines and professional wear alike",
      "BUILDABLE COVERAGE WITH PORE-BLURRING MAKEUP EFFECT: Achieve flawless skin with this buildable coverage formula that allows layering from sheer to medium without cakiness. It smooths texture, blurs pores, and enhances tone evenly\u2014perfect for a natural radiant finish that lasts",
      "LIGHTWEIGHT TEXTURE THAT LOCKS IN HYDRATION ALL DAY: This lightweight cushion foundation is infused with hydrating ingredients, making it ideal for makeup for dry skin and sensitive skin. It provides long-lasting cushion comfort with a breathable feel and dewy glow that lasts from morning to night",
      "MESH CUSHION PUFF SYSTEM FOR PRECISE APPLICATION: Designed with a mesh cushion puff, the system delivers just the right amount of product for pore-blurring makeup and a smooth, even finish. The skin-fit puff adapts to facial curves, making touch-ups effortless and hygienic",
      "30 SHADES CUSTOMIZED FOR GLOBAL SKIN TONES: The wide shade range is carefully developed for international users\u2014from fair to deep\u2014with neutral, warm, and cool undertones. This daily foundation is perfect for diverse skin types and tones, ensuring a flawless, radiant finish on every complexion"
    ],
