        {
          "reviewTitle": "PERFECTION IN A COMPACT!!",
          "reviewText": "This is an absolutely AMAZING PRODUCT!! IT WAS SO VERY EASY & FUN TO APPLY WITH THE ENCLOSED POWDER PUFF(BLACK PLUSH APLICATOR) THE COLOR I CHOSE WAS A PERFECT MATCH FOR MY SKIN tone & UNDERTONE, SO COLOR MATCHING WAS EASY TO FIND THE PERFECT SHADE FOR ANY COLOR OR TONE OF SKIN I ALSO HAVE SENSITIVE SKIN AND THIS DID NOT AFFECT IT AT ALL NO BREAKOUTS! I WAS ABLE TO APPLY IT STRAIGHT OUT OF THE COMPACT AS SOON AS I OPENED IT AND REMOVED THE PROTECTIVE STICKER THAT COVERED IT, TOOK ONLY MINUTES TO DO MY ENTIRE FACE, INCLUDING AROUND THE EYS AND A BIT DOWN TO MY NECK TO EVENLY BLEND IT OUT! LOOKS JUST LIKE SKIN FEELS GREAT TOO! SO LIGHTWEGHT FEELS LIKE YOU ARE WEARING NOTHING ON YOUR SKIN YET THE COVERAGE WAS JUST AMAZING, I DID NOT HAVE TO USE ANY CONCEALER OR PRIMER, BUT I'M GOING TO TRY THOSE NEXT TIME TO SEE IF IT MAKES IT LOOK EVEN BETTER THAN IT ALREADY DID ON IT'S OWN! IT WILL ALSO BE PERFECT FOR QUICK TOUCH-UPS ON THE GO, COMPACT IS PERFECT SIZE TO THROW IN YOUR POCKET OR PURSE, IT DOES NOT SPILL OR LEAK ANY PRODUCT WITH ITS PERFECT DESIGN! AND THE ADDED ADDITION OF THE \" MIXING PALETTE\" IS WONDERFUL IF YOU HAVE GOTTEN TOO MUCH ON THE PLUSH APPLICATOR AND YOU CAN ALSO GO BACK TO THIS AREA TO PICK UP A BIT MORE IF YOU NEED IT WITHOUT HAVING TO DIP INTO THE PRODUCT AGAIN, SO IT IS ECONONICAL AS WELL! YOU CAN USE 100% OF THE PRODUCT, WITH ZERO WASTE! I HIGHLY RECCOMEND THIS PRODUCT AND WILL BE USING THIS BRAND AS MY GO TO FOUNDATION FROM NOW ON! BECAUSE OF THE EASE OF USE, PERFECT COLOR MATCH AND LONG LASTING, BEAUTIFUL NATURAL SKIN LOOK, I KNOW OTHER WOMEN WILL TOTALLY LOVE THIS COMPACT AS MUCH AS I DO! AM A USER OF HER PRODUCT FOR LIFE NOW!!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on February 24, 2026",
          "customer": "Michele Connors",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AGZLBUDQESWKJV7MFTC6PH5INUKQ",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
